GOLDEN PATTERNS

 VALIDATION :  BEFOR INSERT
History / logs:  AFTER UPDATE, AFTER DELET
  Inserted values:  NEW.column
 DELETE VALUE : OLD.COLUCM 
 update value : old/new coulume


| Operation | Available |
| --------- | --------- |
| INSERT    | NEW only  |
| DELETE    | OLD only  |
| UPDATE    | BOTH      |
  
Triggers are mostly:

validation
automatic calculations
logging/history
preventing bad operations
